 <p>Update values using weighted averages</p>
 <p class="eq" style="border-left:solid 1pt black; margin-left:24pt; padding-left:3pt;">
  <var>θ</var>
  <sub>n+1</sub>
  =
  <span class="eq">
   <var>θ</var>
   <sub>i</sub>
   +
   <span class="dvc">
    <var>h</var>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
